{"tid":2305104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍兩次「了不起」讚中國電影︰第一個影院恢復營業","createTime":"2020-11-29T10:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T11:20:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"425ae46165df5365ef263b9b9a83d864b0d1e4cb","tid":2305104,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"《第33屆金雞獎頒獎禮》今日（28/11）在廈門舉行，嘉賓之一的成龍雖然未有行紅地氈，但就開幕不久就接受主持人訪問，他坦言2020年是很難捱的一年，特別是電影行業，但中國電影人夠團結，迎難而上。<br />\n<br />\n成龍除了指今年是不平凡的一年，也喜見中國電影人的團結。「我們中國電影人抱團在一起，讓我們成為世界第一個影院恢復營業、電影恢復生產的國家。」期間大哥更以2次「了不起」，來讚揚中國電影人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，劉德華接受訪問時，坦言想中國與香港的電影人有更多交流：「我是在香港長大，我們的電影還是跟這邊的題材、手法不一樣，希望多跟他們學習，也希望把我們以前的經驗分享給大家。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201128/409462742416625664704526.jpeg/bNca7I7BL0KZJWH3cKScvyPkEzKx15H0adDjFGnQ4xQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201128%2F409462742416625664704526.jpeg%2FbNca7I7BL0KZJWH3cKScvyPkEzKx15H0adDjFGnQ4xQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=49db2c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201128/409464589944623104745192.jpeg/7depjBHChDL9Yc2B26-nWqBXgABhmu7rx3hpwcd4acE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201128%2F409464589944623104745192.jpeg%2F7depjBHChDL9Yc2B26-nWqBXgABhmu7rx3hpwcd4acE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8d7639d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c639f4c073b454e02e82ac011d47e58436c7c5c","tid":2305104,"uid":79117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"588410d4273fe21327f3fa0bf693cb51528f71a4","tid":2305104,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c639f4c073b454e02e82ac011d47e58436c7c5c","tid":2305104,"uid":79117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no